snippet.title: Leonardo DiCaprio Girlfriends List: Dating History
snippet.description:
Leonardo DiCaprio – an american idol of girls and women from all over the world. Let's find out how many hearts this handsome man has broken!
Bridget Hall
1994
When Leo was 20 years old, this professional model became his first girlfriend.
Naomi Campbell
1995
Black Pantera had a short romantic affair with DiCaprio. Now they spend time together as friends.
Kristen Zang
1996
An American model has attended an official event with DiCaprio. But after the release of Titanic the lovers split up.
Demi Moore
1997
The actress could not resist the charms of young and handsome Leo.
Helena Christensen
1997
Victoria's Secret model was the actor`s companion at several parties.
Amber Valletta
1998
If to believe the gossips, Leo saw her photo in a magazine. Then he asked his agent to find her.
Eva Herzigova
1998
A model from Czech has been dating Dicaprio for two months.
Paris Hilton
2000
We are not sure whether they were dating, but these two attended the same parties too many times.
Gisele Bundchen
2000 - 2005
An actress and supermodel from Brazil accompanied Leo at the Oscars. That was the first long-lasting relationship for the celebrity! Nevertheless, this beautiful couple split up. Gisele admitted they needed different things in life.
Bar Refaeli
2005 - 2011
Israeli model has been dating Titanic’s star for six years. Sometimes they took time out. In May 2011 they finally broke up.
Anne Vyalitsyna
2009
A Russian model helped the actor brighten up his life after previous relations.
Blake Lively
2011
An actress, recognized for her role of Serena in the Gossip Girl series, had a 5-month affair with DiCaprio.
Erin Heatherton
2011 - 2012
Leo is really fond of Victoria's Secret angels!
Kat Torres
2013
Brazilian beauty queen met Leonardo in Cannes. They have been dating for a short period of time in October.
Toni Garrn
2013 - 2014
A German model had an 18-month relationship with 40-years-old actor. They had 28-year-age difference!
Kelly Rohrbach
2015
This girl from modeling business and Leonardo have been together for a year. It was really true love! The couple even announced their engagement. Nevertheless, they broke up. The reason – busy schedule of both of them.
Rihanna
January 2016
Dicaprio has spent too many parties with Riri. Was it just friendship or something more?
Nina Agdal
2016 - 2017
Danish model started a relationship with the actor when she was 24 years old. But still, Leo did not mind even a younger lover.
Camila Morrone
2017 till present
An American-Argentinian actress and model started another love-story with the award-winning actor when she was 20 years old. As she says, she is not bothered with the age gap. So, finally, we are waiting for the engagement!

Do you want to see more?
